data.description: This home in the heart of Bridgeport features many updates including New HVAC, New Water Heater, New Storm Doors, Freshly Painted, Gorgeous Hard Wood Floors and More! This is your forever home. With city convenience, this 3 bedroom 1.5 bath has a very spacious interior with lots of class and character. Updated kitchen with hardware, large living room and plenty of room to grow and entertain. The side porch and level yard are perfect for enjoying the sunshine this summer! This one will go fast! Schedule your appointment to see it today!
